            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pan Mexco, tlacualli tlen quihuica ce canahya zo miac canahya, tlacualli tlen tlahuel monequi huan temacah para ma quihuicacan huan quicuazceh quiahuac.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
